  "comment": "12x3W RGB/FC high-power PAR LED\n\nLumiPar 12UTRI is a super-slim PAR LED designed to be a multi-use wash light for events and club installations. Equipped with 12x3W high-efficiency RGB/full colour LED light source, conceived to create bright, intense and saturated colours.\nLumiPar 12UTRI is compatible with the infrared remote controller for intuitive and interactive use without the need of any external DMX units. LumiPar 12UTRI can be also controlled wirelessly through the optional USB WIFI transceiver in combination with WIFIBOX and the SmartColor app.",
